Dataset Download (Simple way)
For Bitcoin (Elliptic)

Open Kaggle in browser

Search: Elliptic Data Set

Click Download ZIP

Extract ZIP → you’ll see files:

elliptic_txs_features.csv

elliptic_txs_classes.csv

elliptic_txs_edgelist.csv (not needed for transformer training)

For Ethereum Fraud

Search on Kaggle: Ethereum Fraud Detection

Download ZIP

Extract ZIP → you may see a file like:

transaction_dataset.csv or ethereum_fraud.csv or Ethereum_Fraud_Detection.csv
(Use the one that contains a fraud label column like FLAG or isFraud)

2️⃣ Add Conversion Script (convert_data.py)

Place it in your project root folder.
